Package org.cytoscape.work.properties

Interface TunablePropertyHandler

  • All Superinterfaces:
    TunableHandler
    public interface TunablePropertyHandler
extends TunableHandler
    An extension of TunableHandler with added functionality to support converting to/from a String.

    Module: work-api

    To use this in your app, include the following dependency in your POM:

    <dependency>
    <groupId>org.cytoscape</groupId>
    <artifactId>work-api</artifactId>
</dependency>

    Cytoscape Backwards Compatibility (SPI Interface): We expect that this interface will be implemented. Therefore to maintain backwards compatibility this interface will only be modified for major version updates.
